---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Master Guide to Finding and Using Digital Coupon Codes Online">
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 sm:py-12">
    {/* Hero Section */}
    <div class="relative mb-8 sm:mb-12">
      <img 
        src="/images/blog/digital-coupon-codes.jpg"
        alt="Digital Coupon Codes Online"
        class="w-full h-[300px] sm:h-[500px] object-cover rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl shadow-lg"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-4 sm:p-8">
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-2 sm:mb-4 leading-tight">
          Master Guide to Finding and Using Digital Coupon Codes Online
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-200 text-base sm:text-lg mb-2">Published on December 9, 2024</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Article Content */}
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      {/* Introduction */}
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        In today's digital shopping landscape, mastering the art of finding and applying digital coupon codes online can lead to significant savings on your purchases. This comprehensive guide will show you how to become an expert at discovering and maximizing digital discount opportunities.
      </p>

      {/* Main Content Sections */}
      <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Where to Find Digital Coupon Codes
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            The first step in mastering digital couponing is knowing where to look for legitimate coupon codes online:
          </p>
          <ul class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6 space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Dedicated coupon websites and databases</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Retailer email newsletters and loyalty programs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Browser extensions that automatically find and apply codes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Social media accounts of your favorite brands</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
              <span>Deal forums and online shopping communities</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Verifying Coupon Code Authenticity
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Not all digital coupon codes you find online are valid or current. Here's how to verify their authenticity:
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Check Before Using</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Check expiration dates and terms of use</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Verify the source is reputable</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Verify Legitimacy</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Look for recent user reviews and success rates</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Be wary of codes that seem too good to be true</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Maximizing Digital Coupon Savings
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            To get the most value from digital coupon codes online, follow these expert strategies:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-primary/10 rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-8">
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">1</span>
                <span>Stack coupon codes with cashback offers when possible</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">2</span>
                <span>Time your purchases during major sales events</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">3</span>
                <span>Compare prices across multiple retailers</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">4</span>
                <span>Sign up for price drop alerts</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center text-primary mr-3">5</span>
                <span>Use virtual shopping carts to track prices over time</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Common Digital Coupon Code Types
          </h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-100">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3">Percentage Off</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base">Get a percentage discount on your total purchase amount</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-100">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3">Fixed Amount</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base">Receive a specific dollar amount off your order</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6 border border-gray-100">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3">Free Shipping</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base">Eliminate shipping costs on your order</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Digital Coupon Code Best Practices
          </h2>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-8">
            <ul class="space-y-4">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Clear your browser cache before applying codes</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Read the fine print for exclusions and limitations</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Take screenshots of successful code applications</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span>Keep track of used codes and their expiration dates</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        {/* Final Tips Section */}
        <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-gray-100 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 sm:mb-6">
            Final Tips for Digital Coupon Code Success
          </h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3">Before Purchase</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Always search for codes before completing a purchase</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Combine multiple savings strategies when possible</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 sm:p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2 sm:mb-3">Stay Organized</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Keep your favorite coupon sources organized</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <span class="text-primary mr-2">•</span>
                  <span>Share successful codes with trusted shopping communities</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>

      {/* Conclusion */}
      <div class="mt-8 sm:mt-12 p-4 sm:p-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl">
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          By following this comprehensive guide to digital coupon codes online, you'll be well-equipped to save money on virtually every online purchase. Remember to bookmark your favorite coupon sources and regularly check for new offers to maximize your savings potential.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Custom styling for better visual hierarchy */
  .prose h2 {
    @apply font-display;
    scroll-margin-top: 100px;
  }
  
  .prose p {
    @apply leading-relaxed text-gray-600;
  }

  .prose ul {
    @apply my-4 sm:my-6;
  }

  .prose li {
    @apply text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base;
  }

  /* Smooth scroll behavior for anchor links */
  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  /* Better touch targets on mobile */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .prose li {
      @apply py-1;
    }
    
    .prose a {
      @apply py-2;
    }
  }
</style>
